  28             ExtendedWindowStyle.WS_EX_DEFAULT, GetSystemColor(SystemColor.COLOR_MENU), string(), Point(), Size(0, initialHeight), Dock.top, Anchors.none), 
  29             font(font_), textColor(GetSystemColor(SystemColor.COLOR_MENUTEXT)), mouseOverColor(201u, 222u, 245u), menuOpenColor(Color.White()),

  32             format(StringAlignment.near, StringAlignment.near, HotKeyPrefix.show), flags(Flags.none), children(this),

  45         public override nothrow Padding DefaultPadding() const
  46         {
  47             return Padding(6, 2, 6, 2);
  48         }
  49         protected override void OnPaint(PaintEventArgs& args)
  50         {
  51             base->OnPaint(args);
  52             args.graphics.Clear(BackgroundColor());
  53             if (MenuChanged())
  54             {
  55                 ResetMenuChanged();
  56                 CollectShortcuts();
  57                 Size size = GetSize();
  58                 size.h = cast<int>(font.GetHeight(args.graphics));
  59                 size.h = size.h + DefaultPadding().Vertical();
  60                 SetSize(size);
  61                 LocateMenuItems(args.graphics, size);
  62             }
  63             DrawChildren(args);
  64         }
  65         private void LocateMenuItems(Graphics& graphics, const Size& size)
  66         {
  67             Rect itemRect(Location(), Size(0, size.h));
  68             Padding padding = DefaultPadding();
  69             PointF origin(0, 0);
  70             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
  71             while (child != null)
  72             {
  73                 if (child is MenuItem*)
  74                 {
  75                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
  76                     Padding menuItemPadding = menuItem->DefaultPadding();
  77                     RectF r = graphics.MeasureStringChecked(menuItem->Text(), font, origin, format);
  78                     int w = cast<int>(r.size.w) + padding.Horizontal() + menuItemPadding.Horizontal();
  79                     itemRect.size.w = w;
  80                     menuItem->SetLocation(itemRect.location);
  81                     menuItem->SetSize(itemRect.size);
  82                     menuItem->CalculateChildRect(graphics, font, format, Point(itemRect.location.x, itemRect.location.y + itemRect.size.h));
  83                     itemRect.location.x = itemRect.location.x + w;
  84                 }
  85                 child = child->NextSibling();
  86             }
  87         }
  88         private void InvalidateParentRect(const Rect& parentRect)
  89         {
  90             Container* container = GetContainer();
  91             if (container != null)
  92             {
  93                 Component* parent = container->Parent();
  94                 if (parent != null && (parent is Control*))
  95                 {
  96                     Control* parentControl = cast<Control*>(parent);
  97                     parentControl->Invalidate(parentRect.ToWinRect());
  98                 }
  99             }
 100         }
 101         private void DrawChildren(PaintEventArgs& args)
 102         {
 103             Graphics ownerWindowGraphics;
 104             Container* container = GetContainer();
 105             if (container != null)
 106             {
 107                 Component* parent = container->Parent();
 108                 if (parent != null && (parent is Control*))
 109                 {
 110                     Control* parentControl = cast<Control*>(parent);
 111                     ownerWindowGraphics = Graphics(parentControl->GetDC());
 112                 }
 113             }
 114             Padding padding = DefaultPadding();
 115             Size size = GetSize();
 116             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 117             while (child != null)
 118             {
 119                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 120                 {
 121                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 122                     menuItem->Draw(args.graphics, padding, textBrush, backgroundBrush, mouseOverBrush, menuOpenBrush, shadowBrush, blackBrush, blackPen, darkPen, font, format, 
 123                         ownerWindowGraphics, menuOpenColor, this);
 124                 }
 125                 child = child->NextSibling();
 126             }

 132         protected override void OnKeyDown(KeyEventArgs& args)
 133         {
 134             base->OnKeyDown(args);
 135             if (!args.handled)
 136             {
 137                 HashMap<Keys, MenuItem*>.ConstIterator it = shortcuts.CFind(args.keyData);
 138                 if (it != shortcuts.CEnd())
 139                 {
 140                     MenuItem* menuItem = it->second;
 141                     menuItem->DoClick();
 142                     args.handled = true;
 143                 }
 144             }

 150         protected override void OnMouseMove(MouseEventArgs& args)
 151         {
 152             base->OnMouseMove(args);
 153             bool handled = false;
 154             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 155             while (child != null)
 156             {
 157                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 158                 {
 159                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 160                     if (!menuItem->Contains(args.location))
 161                     {
 162                         menuItem->ResetSelected();
 163                         if (menuItem->MouseInClient())
 164                         {
 165                             menuItem->ResetMouseInClient();
 166                             menuItem->DoMouseLeave();
 167                         }
 168                     }
 169                 }
 170                 child = child->NextSibling();
 171             }
 172             child = children.FirstChild();
 173             while (child != null)
 174             {
 175                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 176                 {
 177                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 178                     if (menuItem->Contains(args.location))
 179                     {
 180                         menuItem->SetSelected();
 181                         if (!menuItem->MouseInClient())
 182                         {
 183                             menuItem->SetMouseInClient();
 184                             menuItem->DoMouseEnter(IsOpen(), this);
 185                         }
 186                         else
 187                         {
 188                             menuItem->DoMouseMove(args);
 189                         }
 190                         handled = true;
 191                     }
 192                 }
 193                 child = child->NextSibling();
 194             }
 195             if (!handled)
 196             {
 197                 if (IsOpen())
 198                 {
 199                     if (latestOpenedMenuItem != null)
 200                     {
 201                         Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 202                         while (child != null && !handled)
 203                         {
 204                             if (child is MenuItem*)
 205                             {
 206                                 MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 207                                 if (menuItem->IsSameOrParentOf(latestOpenedMenuItem))
 208                                 {
 209                                     menuItem->DispatchMouseMove(args, handled, this);
 210                                 }
 211                             }
 212                             child = child->NextSibling();
 213                         }
 214                     }
 215                 }
 216             }
 217         }
 218         protected override void OnMouseLeave()
 219         {
 220             base->OnMouseLeave();
 221             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 222             while (child != null)
 223             {
 224                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 225                 {
 226                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 227                     if (menuItem->MouseInClient() || menuItem->Children().IsEmpty())
 228                     {
 229                         menuItem->ResetSelected();
 230                         menuItem->ResetMouseInClient();
 231                         Point mousePos;
 232                         WinGetMessagePos(mousePos.x, mousePos.y);
 233                         mousePos = ScreenToClient(mousePos);
 234                         if (menuItem != latestOpenedMenuItem || !menuItem->UnionRectContains(mousePos))
 235                         {
 236                             menuItem->DoMouseLeave();
 237                         }
 238                     }
 239                     else
 240                     {
 241                         menuItem->ResetSelected();
 242                         menuItem->ResetMouseInClient();
 243                     }
 244                 }
 245                 child = child->NextSibling();
 246             }
 247             InvalidateMenu();
 248         }
 249         internal void InvalidateMenu()
 250         {
 251             Invalidate();
 252             Rect menuRect;
 253             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 254             while (child != null)
 255             {
 256                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 257                 {
 258                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 259                     menuItem->GetUnionRect(menuRect);
 260                 }
 261                 child = child->NextSibling();
 262             }
 263             InvalidateParentRect(menuRect);
 264         }

 268             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 269             while (child != null)
 270             {
 271                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 272                 {
 273                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 274                     menuItem->CollectShortcuts(shortcuts);
 275                 }
 276                 child = child->NextSibling();
 277             }

 279         internal bool HandleAccessKey(wchar accessKey, Keys keyCode, bool& wantsKeys)
 280         {
 281             LogView* logView = Application.GetLogView();
 282             if (logView != null)
 283             {
 284                 string s = "MENUBAR: access key = '" + ToString(accessKey) + "' " + ToHexString(cast<ushort>(accessKey)) + ", key code = " + string(keyCodeStr[cast<int>(keyCode)]);
 285                 logView->WriteLine(s);
 286             }
 287             if (accessKey == '\0' && keyCode == Keys.none)
 288             {
 289                 if (selectedMenuItem == null)
 290                 {
 291                     MenuItem* firstMenuItem = GetFirstMenuItem();
 292                     if (firstMenuItem != null)
 293                     {
 294                         SetSelectedMenuItem(firstMenuItem);
 295                         wantsKeys = true;
 296                         Invalidate();
 297                         return true;
 298                     }
 299                 }
 300                 else
 301                 {
 302                     MenuItem* openedMenuItem = GetOpenedMenuItem();
 303                     if (openedMenuItem != null)
 304                     {
 305                         openedMenuItem->SetState(MenuItem.State.closed);
 306                     }
 307                     selectedMenuItem->ResetSelected();
 308                     SetSelectedMenuItem(null);
 309                     wantsKeys = false;
 310                     Invalidate();
 311                     return true;
 312                 }
 313             }
 314             else if (accessKey != '\0' && keyCode == Keys.none)
 315             {
 316                 MenuItem* menuItem = GetMenuItemByAccessKey(accessKey);
 317                 if (menuItem != null)
 318                 {
 319                     MenuItem* firstMenuItem = menuItem->GetFirstMenuItem();
 320                     if (firstMenuItem != null)
 321                     {
 322                         if (selectedMenuItem != null)
 323                         {
 324                             MenuItem* openedMenuItem = GetOpenedMenuItem();
 325                             if (openedMenuItem != null)
 326                             {
 327                                 openedMenuItem->SetState(MenuItem.State.closed);
 328                             }
 329                         }
 330                         menuItem->SetState(MenuItem.State.open);
 331                         SetSelectedMenuItem(firstMenuItem);
 332                         wantsKeys = true;
 333                         Invalidate();
 334                         return true;
 335                     }
 336                 }
 337             }
 338             else if (accessKey == '\0' && keyCode != Keys.none)
 339             {
 340                 if (keyCode == Keys.menu)
 341                 {
 342                     wantsKeys = true;
 343                     return true;
 344                 }
 345                 else
 346                 {
 347                     if (selectedMenuItem != null)
 348                     {
 349                         MenuItem* parentItem = selectedMenuItem->GetParentMenuItem();
 350                         bool handled = selectedMenuItem->HandleKey(keyCode, wantsKeys, parentItem, this);
 351                         return handled;
 352                     }
 353                 }
 354             }
 355             wantsKeys = false;
 356             return false;
 357         }

 362         protected override void OnMouseDown(MouseEventArgs& args)
 363         {
 364             base->OnMouseDown(args);
 365             SetLatestMouseDownMenuItem(null);
 366             bool handled = false;
 367             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 368             while (child != null)
 369             {
 370                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 371                 {
 372                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 373                     menuItem->DoMouseDown(args, handled, this);
 374                     if (handled)
 375                     {
 376                         InvalidateMenu();
 377                         return;
 378                     }
 379                 }
 380                 child = child->NextSibling();
 381             }
 382             if (IsOpen())
 383             {
 384                 SetClosed();
 385                 SetLatestOpenedMenuItem(null);
 386                 Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 387                 while (child != null)
 388                 {
 389                     if (child is MenuItem*)
 390                     {
 391                         MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 392                         menuItem->SetState(MenuItem.State.closed);
 393                     }
 394                     child = child->NextSibling();
 395                 }
 396                 InvalidateMenu();
 397             }
 398         }

 509         private inline nothrow bool MenuChanged()
 510         {
 511             return (flags & Flags.menuChanged) != Flags.none;
 512         }
 513         internal inline nothrow void SetMenuChanged()
 514         {
 515             flags = cast<Flags>(flags | Flags.menuChanged);
 516         }
 517         private inline nothrow void ResetMenuChanged()
 518         {
 519             flags = cast<Flags>(flags & ~Flags.menuChanged);
 520         }
 521         internal inline nothrow bool IsOpen() const
 522         {
 523             return (flags & Flags.open) != Flags.none;
 524         }
 525         public inline nothrow void SetOpen()
 526         {
 527             flags = cast<Flags>(flags | Flags.open);
 528         }
 529         public void SetClosed()
 530         {
 531             if (IsOpen())

 535             }

 559     public abstract class MenuItemBase : Component
 560     {
 561         public nothrow MenuItemBase() : level(0), location(), size()
 562         {
 563         }
 564         public abstract void Draw(Graphics& graphics, const Padding& parentPadding, const Brush& textBrush, const Brush& backgroundBrush, const Brush& mouseOverBrush, 
 565             const Brush& menuOpenBrush, const Brush& shadowBrush, const Brush& blackBrush, const Pen& blackPen, const Pen& darkPen, const Font& font, const StringFormat& format, 
 566             Graphics& ownerWindowGraphics, const Color& ownerWindowBackgrounColor, MenuBar* menuBar);
 567         internal nothrow MenuItem* GetParentMenuItem() const
 568         {
 569             Container* container = GetContainer();
 570             if (container != null)
 571             {
 572                 Component* parent = container->Parent();
 573                 if (parent != null)

 736         internal bool HandleKey(Keys key, bool& wantsKeys, MenuItem* parentMenuItem, MenuBar* menuBar)
 737         {
 738             if (key >= Keys.a && key <= Keys.z || key >= Keys.d0 && key <= Keys.d9)
 739             {
 740                 wchar accessKey = cast<wchar>(cast<int>(key));
 741                 MenuItem* childItem = null;

 743                 {
 744                     childItem = parentMenuItem->GetChildItemByAccessKey(accessKey);
 745                 }

 748                     childItem = menuBar->GetMenuItemByAccessKey(accessKey);

 751                 {
 752                     childItem->Execute(parentMenuItem, wantsKeys, menuBar);

1141         internal void DoMouseDown(MouseEventArgs& args, bool& handled, MenuBar* menuBar)
1142         {

1173                             childItem->DoMouseDown(args, handled, menuBar);

1190                             {

1204                                         DoMouseDown(args, menuBar);
1205                                         handled = true;
1206                                     }
1207                                 }
1208                                 else

1505         public void CalculateChildRect(Graphics& graphics, const Font& font, const StringFormat& format, const Point& location)

1928         private void DrawChildIndicator(Graphics& graphics, const Brush& blackBrush)
1929         {
1930             if (children.IsEmpty()) return;
1931             Point loc = Location();
1932             Size size = GetSize();
1933             int childIndicatorIndent = ChildIndicatorIndent();
1934             int childIndicatorWidth = ChildIndicatorWidth();
1935             int shadowWidth = ShadowWidth();
1936             Point up(loc.x + size.w - childIndicatorIndent - shadowWidth, loc.y + size.h / 2 - childIndicatorWidth / 2);
1937             Point down(loc.x + size.w - childIndicatorIndent - shadowWidth, loc.y + size.h / 2 + childIndicatorWidth / 2);
1938             Point right(loc.x + size.w - childIndicatorIndent + cast<int>((Sqrt(3) / 2.0) * childIndicatorWidth) - shadowWidth, loc.y + size.h / 2);
1939             List<Point> triangle;
1940             triangle.Add(up);
1941             triangle.Add(down);
1942             triangle.Add(right);
1943             graphics.FillPolygonChecked(blackBrush, 3, triangle.Begin().Ptr());
1944 
1945         }
